00:01:22.580 --> 00:01:27.040
and the Sadducees, two Judaiyan 
groups that Jesus contended with

00:01:27.040 --> 00:01:30.100
primarily in and around Jerusalem and
the temple.

00:01:30.100 --> 00:01:33.830
Now to simplify a complicated comparison,
Pharisees

00:01:33.830 --> 00:01:39.660
represented mainstream Judaism and... [jokes] they had a really great passing game...

00:01:40.200 --> 00:01:42.420
