interpretation

00:03:23.200 --> 00:03:27.519
of biblical doctrine. This of course was
seen as defiant

00:03:27.519 --> 00:03:32.989
and an insult too Sadducees. Challenging their power and way of life

00:03:32.989 --> 00:03:36.180
and ultimately became part of why they
wanted Jesus arrested.

